
  Mareanie    Poison Type Pokémon

  It plunges the poison spike 
  on its head into its prey.  When 
  the prey has weakened, Mareanie 
  deals the finishing blow with 
  its 10 tentacles. 
	Evolution Chain
      Mareanie ► Toxapex

